tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I was looking for a dentist for my 7-yr old son.. he had pain in multiple teeth and though it was urgent I was worried about the consequences of landing into the wrong clinic. But once I came to this clinic I felt positive vibes. Doctor was very humble and showed empathy. She diagnosed the problem well and proposed the correct line of treatment and further executed to perfection. Her soft skills are exceptional when it comes to handling kids. One more thing to note is that she has all the time to answer your queries to satisfaction and is not in a hurry at all. The staff also is well equipped to look after kids during procedures. End of the day, am happy to have landed here.. good job by doctor and support staff, keep it up!
Regards,
Asif A R Shaikh

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Value for money,Wait time,
